{{vgname2|任天堂3DS|en=Nintendo 3DS|ja=ニンテンドー3DS|簡稱「'''N3DS'''」或「'''3DS'''」}}，是[[任天堂|任天堂]]于2011年至2020年推出的[[攜帶型遊戲機|攜帶型遊戲機]]，為[[任天堂DS|任天堂DS]]的后续机种。最大特點是利用了[[视差障壁|视差障壁]]技術，讓使用者不需配戴任何[[3D眼鏡|特殊眼鏡]]即可裸眼感受到立體[[3D|3D]]圖像效果。<ref name="announcement">{{cite press release |url=http://www.nintendo.co.jp/ir/pdf/2010/100323e.pdf |title=Launch of New Portable Game Machine |date=2010-03-23 |publisher=Nintendo |accessdate=2010-03-23 |location=[[京都|京都]] |archive-date=2019-09-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190911193136/https://www.nintendo.co.jp/ir/pdf/2010/100323e.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>该平台[[向下兼容|向下兼容]][[任天堂DS|任天堂DS]]和[[任天堂DSi|任天堂DSi]]的軟體。<ref name="announcement" />

任天堂3DS有五个衍生机型，分别是2012年7月发售的大屏幕版本任天堂3DS LL/XL；2013年10月在欧美发售的廉价型号[[任天堂2DS|任天堂2DS]]；2014年10月起在日本发售的[[新任天堂3DS|新任天堂3DS]]与新任天堂3DS LL/XL；以及于2017年7月起发售的[[新任天堂2DS_XL|新任天堂2DS XL]]。

2012年9月28日台灣以及香港地區同步發行繁體中文版的「Nintendo 3DS」以及「Nintendo 3DS XL」。2012年11月1日中国[[大陆地区|大陆地区]]由[[神游科技|神游科技]]发行的简体中文版“iQue 3DS XL”（神游DS双屏互动多媒体系统）主机正式公布，12月1日起陆续供货发售。

== 歷史 ==
[[File:Virtual_Boy_and_3DS_(picture_4).jpg|任天堂3DS以及Virtual Boy。]]
自從1980年代以來，任天堂就已經嘗試過不少立體3D技術。而在1988年於[[FC磁碟機|FC磁碟機]]發行的《任天堂方程式賽車 2：3D 拉力賽》（Famicom Grand Prix II: 3D Hot Rally）是任天堂首次嘗試運用立體3D技術的首款遊戲，玩家只要在螢幕使用特殊眼鏡觀看特別畫像就會有3D效果。<ref name=IwataAsks3DS1>{{cite web |url=http://www.nintendo.co.uk/NOE/en_GB/news/iwata/iwata_asks_-_nintendo_3ds_30756_30757.html#top |title=Iwata Asks: Nintendo 3DS |accessdate=2011-01-12 |quote='''Miyamoto:''' I suppose so. To go way back, I even made a 3D Famicom game on disk that you played wearing goggles. We made that with you, Iwata-san. '''Iwata:''' Right, right! The first work Miyamoto-san and I did together was a racing game for the Family Computer Disk System that you played wearing goggles. [...] A game called Famicom Grand Prix II: 3D Hot Rally. |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/65QYop6GI?url=http://www.nintendo.co.uk/NOE/en_GB/news/iwata/iwata_asks_-_nintendo_3ds_30756_30757.html#top |archivedate=2012-02-13 }}</ref>而在1995年，[[Game_Boy|Game Boy]]的發明者[[橫井軍平|橫井軍平]]則著手開發首款具備立體3D影像功能的[[Virtual_Boy|Virtual Boy]]主機，然而該主機發售日期比預期早了許多，使得任天堂得以空出更多資源研發新主機[[任天堂64|任天堂64]]，最後VB這款商品在商業上表現得非常失敗，是任天堂歷史上銷量最低的遊戲主機。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.gamepro.com/article/features/111823/the-10-worst-selling-consoles-of-all-time-page-2-of-2/ |title=The 10 Worst-Selling Consoles of All Time |accessdate=2007-11-25 |author=Blake Snow |publisher=[[GamePro|GamePro]] |date=2007-05-04 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080905175411/http://www.gamepro.com/article/features/111823/the-10-worst-selling-consoles-of-all-time-page-2-of-2/ |archivedate=2008-09-05 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref>''Game Over: How Nintendo Zapped an American Industry, Captured Your Dollars, and Enslaved Your Children'' by David Sheff, 1993, Random House.</ref><ref name=IwataAsks3DS2>{{cite web|url=http://www.nintendo.co.uk/NOE/en_GB/news/iwata/iwata_asks_-_nintendo_3ds_30756_30757.html#top|title=Iwata Asks: Nintendo 3DS|accessdate=2011-01-12|quote='''Iwata:''' Virtual Boy was, I think, a commercial failure. Normally, I think it would have been understandable if Nintendo experienced a kind of trauma with regard to the whole 3D genre. But Nintendo continued to doggedly make attempts in 3D technology. And you could say that those attempts have now finally borne fruit. I feel like that is an interesting progression of topicsyay.|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/65QYop6GI?url=http://www.nintendo.co.uk/NOE/en_GB/news/iwata/iwata_asks_-_nintendo_3ds_30756_30757.html#top|archivedate=2012-02-13}}</ref>[[宮本茂|宮本茂]]曾表示他並不滿意VB主機所表現的線條模型和主機的實用性，不過他卻覺得這個設計概念是很先進的。<ref name=IwataAsks3DS3>{{cite web |url=http://www.nintendo.co.uk/NOE/en_GB/news/iwata/iwata_asks_-_nintendo_3ds_30756_30757.html#top |title=Iwata Asks: Nintendo 3DS |accessdate=2011-01-12 |quote='''Miyamoto:''' At the time, as I was working on the Nintendo 64 system, part of me thought we should use wire frames to render 3D graphics, but I also thought that wire frame images weren't terribly appealing. [...] If nothing but wire-frame fighter craft had appeared and Mario and other beloved characters had never shown up, that would be a little sad. But if you only changed the depth of a 2D image of Mario, it wouldn't bring out the real appeal of Virtual Boy. So the Virtual Boy system was a complicated affair. [...] Virtual Boy had two big tasks to accomplish, and it went out into the world without satisfying either one. It's not so much that the machine itself was wrong as a product, but that we were wrong in how we portrayed it. |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/65QYop6GI?url=http://www.nintendo.co.uk/NOE/en_GB/news/iwata/iwata_asks_-_nintendo_3ds_30756_30757.html#top |archivedate=2012-02-13 }}</ref>

VB主機的失敗讓任天堂一度懷疑立體3D遊戲的可行性<ref>{{cite web |url=http://kotaku.com/5745178/nintendo-traumatized-by-3d-virtual-boy-but-laughs-about-it-now |title=Nintendo 'Traumatized' By 3D Virtual Boy, But '(Laughs)' About It Now |publisher=Kotaku |accessdate=2012-06-10 |archive-date=2018-11-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181120021559/https://kotaku.com/5745178/nintendo-traumatized-by-3d-virtual-boy-but-laughs-about-it-now |dead-url=no }}</ref>，儘管如此，任天堂還是在其他產品上深入研究3D技術。於2001年發售的[[任天堂GameCube|任天堂GameCube]]主機是第二款具備立體3D影像的遊戲主機<ref name=IwataAsks3DS4>{{cite web|url=http://www.nintendo.co.uk/NOE/en_GB/news/iwata/iwata_asks_-_nintendo_3ds_30756_30757.html#top|title=Iwata Asks: Nintendo 3DS|quote='''Iwata:''' To go back a little further, the Nintendo GameCube system actually had 3D-compatible circuitry built in [...] '''Itoi:''' Nintendo GameCube did? And all the Nintendo GameCube systems around the world? '''Iwata:''' Yeah. If you fit it with a certain accessory, it could display 3D images.|accessdate=2011-01-11|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/65QYop6GI?url=http://www.nintendo.co.uk/NOE/en_GB/news/iwata/iwata_asks_-_nintendo_3ds_30756_30757.html#top|archivedate=2012-02-13}}</ref>，NGC的性能得以處理立體的3D影像功能，然而最終只有一款遊戲《[[路易吉洋樓|路易吉洋樓]]》展示了這個技術，在當時3D液晶顯示器並不普及，且擁有高昂的價格的年代，這項功能最終沒有使用在成品上。<ref name=IwataAsks3DS5>{{cite web |url=http://www.nintendo.co.uk/NOE/en_GB/news/iwata/iwata_asks_-_nintendo_3ds_30756_30757.html#top |title=Iwata Asks: Nintendo 3DS |accessdate=2011-01-12 |quote='''Iwata:''' We couldn't have done it without selling it for a price far above that of the Nintendo GameCube system itself! We already had a game for it, though – Luigi's Mansion, simultaneously released with Nintendo GameCube Device. |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/65QYop6GI?url=http://www.nintendo.co.uk/NOE/en_GB/news/iwata/iwata_asks_-_nintendo_3ds_30756_30757.html#top |archivedate=2012-02-13 }}</ref>

任天堂後來曾把現在3DS的3D技術使用在GBA上<ref name=IwataAsks3DS6>{{cite web |url=http://www.nintendo.co.uk/NOE/en_GB/news/iwata/iwata_asks_-_nintendo_3ds_30756_30757.html#top |title=Iwata Asks: Nintendo 3DS |accessdate=2011-01-12 |quote='''Iwata:'''For example, a sample screen used in the Nintendo 3DS to illustrate how you can see three-dimensional images without special glasses was functioning on the Game Boy Advance SP system. |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/65QYop6GI?url=http://www.nintendo.co.uk/NOE/en_GB/news/iwata/iwata_asks_-_nintendo_3ds_30756_30757.html#top |archivedate=2012-02-13 }}</ref>，然而任天堂並不滿意這項實驗，因為在當時這樣GBA的螢幕解析度上，並不能精確地表現良好的效果。<ref name=IwataAsks3DS7>{{cite web |url=http://www.nintendo.co.uk/NOE/en_GB/news/iwata/iwata_asks_-_nintendo_3ds_30756_30757.html#top |title=Iwata Asks: Nintendo 3DS |accessdate=2011-01-12 |quote='''Iwata:''' [...] But the resolution of LCD was low then, so it didn't look that great and it never made it to being a product. In order to make images look three-dimensional without special glasses [...] you need high resolution and high-precision technology. We didn't have that to a sufficient degree back then, so the stereoscopic effect wasn't very sharp. |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/65QYop6GI?url=http://www.nintendo.co.uk/NOE/en_GB/news/iwata/iwata_asks_-_nintendo_3ds_30756_30757.html#top |archivedate=2012-02-13 }}</ref>隨著任天堂DS的發展以及山內溥堅持的研究，任天堂成功地在[[小倉百人一首殿堂時雨殿|時雨殿]]主題公園中展示了3D技術<ref name=IwataAsks3DS8>{{cite web |url=http://www.nintendo.co.uk/NOE/en_GB/news/iwata/iwata_asks_-_nintendo_3ds_30756_30757.html#top |title=Iwata Asks: Nintendo 3DS |accessdate=2011-01-12 |quote='''Miyamoto:''' When we were making Shigureden, Yamauchi-san expressed his earnest hope that we could make something "jump out." |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/65QYop6GI?url=http://www.nintendo.co.uk/NOE/en_GB/news/iwata/iwata_asks_-_nintendo_3ds_30756_30757.html#top |archivedate=2012-02-13 }}</ref>，在主題公園的遊客可以使用DS提供的嚮導指南軟體。雖然沒有大量生產，但任天堂擁有豐富的研究和開發經驗，後來用於現在的3DS上。<ref name=IwataAsks3DS9>{{cite web |url=http://www.nintendo.co.uk/NOE/en_GB/news/iwata/iwata_asks_-_nintendo_3ds_30756_30757.html#top |title=Iwata Asks: Nintendo 3DS |accessdate=2011-01-12 |quote='''Miyamoto:''' We got pretty far along with regard to the methodology, but didn't have enough time to develop it and gave up. But we did get to do a lot of research with regard to the liquid crystal and other matters involved. |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/65QYop6GI?url=http://www.nintendo.co.uk/NOE/en_GB/news/iwata/iwata_asks_-_nintendo_3ds_30756_30757.html#top |archivedate=2012-02-13 }}</ref>

=== 背景 ===
在2009年底，就已經有關於DS後續機的一些臆測消息出現，該年10月中旬，新聞媒體「Tech Tabloid」報導了[[圖形處理器|圖形處理器]]（GPU）的生產商[[Nvidia|Nvidia]]已經獲得了新產品將使用該公司處理器產品的合約，並表明新產品將使用Nvidia Tegra系列的單核心晶片。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.brightsideofnews.com/news/2009/10/13/nvidia-tegra-wins-contract-for-next-gen-nintendo-ds.aspx |title=nVidia Tegra wins contract for next-gen Nintendo DS |first=Theo |last=Valich |authorlink=Special:Contributions/Tvalich |date=2009-10-13 |work=Bright Side of News* |publisher=Bright Side Network |accessdate=2010-04-04 |quote=Currently, we have no information what exact chip is being used [just that nVidia won the contract], but with the debut set for February 2010, the second generation of Tegra chips could make an excellent base [to be launched at Mobile World Congress in Barcelona]. |archive-date=2020-05-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200502143045/http://www.brightsideofnews.com/news/2009/10/13/nvidia-tegra-wins-contract-for-next-gen-nintendo-ds.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>一個月之後，岩田聰社長提到了未來任天堂新型的攜帶型遊戲機的一些內容，表示手機的3G行動網路功能並不適合任天堂的玩家們，但對於[[亞馬遜公司|亞馬遜]]所推出的[[kindle|kindle]]產品上的「Whispernet」非常有興趣，因為用戶可以使用免費的3G行動網路進行網路交流。<ref name="Whispernet">{{cite web |url=http://www.ft.com/cms/s/2/04f7ebd8-c571-11de-8193-00144feab49a.html |title=Nintendo considers Kindle tactics for consoles |first=Robin |last=Harding |date=2009-10-30 |work=Financial Times |location=[[Tokyo|Tokyo]], Japan |accessdate=2010-04-04 |quote=In reality, if we did this it would increase the cost of the hardware, and customers would complain about Nintendo putting prices up, but it is one option for the future. |archive-date=2016-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303191850/http://www.ft.com/cms/s/2/04f7ebd8-c571-11de-8193-00144feab49a.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

任天堂表示在釋出DS的原型機之前，就已經對一些攜帶產品的動態感應器、陀螺儀感到興趣<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2004/05/13/technology/taking-the-game-war-to-a-second-front.html?pagewanted=all |title=Taking the Game War To a Second Front |first=Stephen |last=Totilo |date=2004-05-13 |work=The New York Times |publisher=The New York Times Company |accessdate=2010-04-04 |quote=To keep costs down, Mr. Miyamoto said, some features were left out of the DS. Maybe next time, he said, he will be able to include a tilt sensor for gyroscopic control. |archive-date=2021-02-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210205075400/https://www.nytimes.com/2004/05/13/technology/taking-the-game-war-to-a-second-front.html?pagewanted=all |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在2010年1月，據傳岩田聰在[[朝日新聞|朝日新聞]]上的某些評論導致間接證實，任天堂DS的後續機將會加入陀螺儀。<ref name="Kotaku">{{cite web |url=http://kotaku.com/5462023/nintendo-vs-japanese-newspaper-it-continues |title=Nintendo vs. Japanese Newspaper, It Continues! |first=Brian |last=Ashcraft |date=2010-02-02 |work=Kotaku |publisher=Gawker Media |accessdate=2010-04-04 |quote=The exec went on to address the issue with the Asahi Shimbun, asserting that the reporter stated, 'The graphics for the next DS will be highly detailed and it will contain a motion sensor, right?' Iwata claims he then replied, 'Those things are naturally being required. But do you think it would sell with just that?' Iwata emphasized that this last part was left completely out. |archive-date=2018-10-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181004021511/https://kotaku.com/5462023/nintendo-vs-japanese-newspaper-it-continues |dead-url=no }}</ref>2010年2月，一個電視遊戲網站「Computer and Video Games」報導指出DS後續機的軟體開發工具包是優先給予[[神奇寶貝_(企業)|神奇寶貝股份有限公司]]使用，據一間未公布名稱的第三方遊戲工作室透露的內幕，後續機採用了比[[iPhone|iPhone]]動態感應器更好的相似硬體。<ref name="CVG">{{cite web |url=http://www.computerandvideogames.com/235077/ds2-in-the-hands-of-pokemon-company/ |title=DS2 in the hands of Pokemon Company |first=Tim |last=Ingham |date=2010-02-16 |work=[[Computer_and_Video_Games|CVG]] |publisher=Future Publishing |accessdate=2010-04-04 |quote=Any kind of March announcement wouldn't fit with the timeline I understand the second DS to be on,' he added. |archive-date=2014-12-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141207203931/http://www.computerandvideogames.com/235077/ds2-in-the-hands-of-pokemon-company/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2010年3月23日任天堂正式發表新聞稿指出將推出DS主機的後續機「任天堂3DS」。據某些業界人士透露，任天堂發表的新聞稿可能是為了分散剛推出不久的[[任天堂DS#.E4.BB.BB.E5.A4.A9.E5.A0.82DSi_LL|任天堂DSi LL]]注意力，且搶先日本媒體一步發表一些有關新產品的資訊。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.cnbc.com/id/36087758 |title=Did Nintendo Doom New Handheld Before Its Release? |date=2010-03-29 |publisher=[[CNBC|CNBC]] |accessdate=2010-04-03 |quote='Apparently, the Japanese press was all over it and talked with suppliers there and Nintendo just wanted to get out ahead by breaking the news to prevent a leak,' says Billy Pigeon, senior analyst with M2 Research. |archive-date=2011-06-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110611042557/http://www.cnbc.com/id/36087758 |dead-url=no }}</ref>2010年4月，一份由[[三美電機|三美電機]]提交給[[美國聯邦通信委員會|美國聯邦通信委員會]]（FCC）疑似為3DS內部零件硬體的圖片，分析指出3DS的特色可能是使用了DS系列主機從來沒使用過的15：9寬比例螢幕以及一個相當類似[[PlayStation_Portable|PlayStation Portable]]的[[類比搖桿|類比搖桿]]。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://gameusagi.com/?p=1158 |title=3DS Dev-Build Hardware Analysis |first=Logan |last=Predy |date=2010-05-17 |work=Game Usagi |accessdate=2010-05-18 |quote=For their '3D Control Stick' Nintendo has decided to go for something much more akin to the 'control nub' on the PSP systems. |archive-date=2012-04-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120426124412/http://gameusagi.com/?p=1158 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

=== 2010年E3展 ===
[[File:E3_2010_Nintendo_Media_Event_-_Legend_of_Zelda_Skyward_Sword_demo_machines_rise_from_the_floor.jpg|在E3展上公布了相當多主機詳細的內容以及遊戲資訊。]]
2010年6月，電視遊戲網站[[IGN|IGN]]報導說根據「一些有3DS開發經驗的製作人」，指出3DS的系統處理能力「遠遠地超過Wii」，而且它的3D圖形處理器使得遊戲
「能夠接近[[XBOX360|XBOX360]]和[[PlayStation_3|PlayStation 3]]的視覺畫面效果」。他們還說3DS並不使用Nvidia Tegra系列的行動處理晶片。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://ds.ign.com/articles/109/1094930p1.html |title=E3 2010: Everything We Know About the 3DS |first=Craig |last=Harris |date=2010-06-04 |publisher=IGN |accessdate=2010-06-06 |archive-date=2011-01-26 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/5w2IEuyrS?url=http://ds.ign.com/articles/109/1094930p1.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

最後，3DS主機終於在2010年6月15日舉辦的2010年E3展上公開露面。3DS首個公開遊戲畫面的遊戲是《[[新·光神話_帕爾提娜之鏡|新·光神話 帕爾提娜之鏡]]》，其後還公布了許多计划登陆3DS的第三方游戏，包括[[史克威爾艾尼克斯|史克威爾艾尼克斯]]的《[[王國之心_3D_［夢降深處］|王國之心3D]]》、《[[Final_Fantasy|Final Fantasy]]》系列，[[科樂美|科樂美]]的《[[潛龍諜影3：食蛇者|潛龍諜影 食蛇者 3D]]》，[[华纳兄弟互动娱乐|华纳兄弟互动娱乐]]的《蝙蝠俠》，[[育碧軟體|育碧軟體]]的《刺客信条：失落的遗产3D》（后取消开发<ref>[http://3ds.tgbus.com/news/201107/20110718100353.shtml 3DS版《刺客信条：失落的遗产3D》取消开发] {{Wayback|url=http://3ds.tgbus.com/news/201107/20110718100353.shtml |date=20200921105404 }}，[[电玩巴士|电玩巴士]]</ref>），[[卡普空|卡普空]]的《[[惡靈古堡_啟示|惡靈古堡 啟示]]》、《[[超级街头霸王IV_3D|超级街头霸王IV 3D]]》以及[[Activision|Activision]]的《DJ英雄》。在展會结束之後，任天堂又公布了一批准备登陆3DS的游戏，包括《[[瑪利歐賽車7|瑪利歐賽車7]]》、《[[来吧！动物森友会|来吧！动物森友会]]》、《[[星際火狐64_3D|星際火狐64 3D]]》<ref>[http://www.nintendo.com/3ds/games/ Nintendo 3DS – Games at Nintendo] {{WebCite|url=https://www.webcitation.org/6GfmiB6KL?url=http://www.nintendo.com/games/gameGuide;jsessionid=52027DAFC2343961A8B1066F5BA58FE8?system=3ds |date=20130517030511 |dateformat=iso }} Nintendo of America Inc.</ref>以及《[[薩爾達傳說_時之笛_3D|薩爾達傳說 時之笛 3D]]》<ref>{{cite web |url=http://ds.ign.com/articles/109/1098192p1.html |title=E3 2010: Ocarina of Time 3DS On the Way! – Nintendo 3DS News at IGN |publisher=IGN |date=2010-03-29 |accessdate=2010-06-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120308005614/http://ds.ign.com/articles/109/1098192p1.html |archive-date=2012-03-08 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。任天堂3DS最终上市的成品和E3展示的样机有些许出入。<ref>{{cite web |last=Towell |first=Justin |date=2010-08-23 |title=Is the design of the 3DS final or not? Nintendo clears up the confusion |url=http://www.gamesradar.com/is-the-design-of-the-3ds-final-or-not-nintendo-clears-up-the-confusion/ |publisher=GamesRadar UK |accessdate=2010-08-25 |archive-date=2021-02-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210205075501/https://www.gamesradar.com/is-the-design-of-the-3ds-final-or-not-nintendo-clears-up-the-confusion/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

=== 發售前 ===
2010年9月29日，日本任天堂舉辦了「Nintendo Conference 2010」並宣布日本3DS的發售日在2011年2月26日，同時也發表一些3DS的細節，包括內建Mii工作室、懷舊平台（包含[[Game_Boy|Game Boy]]和[[Game_Boy_Color|Game Boy Color]]以及重製的「3D 經典」系列）、充電座、多任务处理、[[擴增實境|擴增實境]]遊戲、附带2GB記憶卡用於儲存遊戲內容以及最終定名的「瞬缘连接」和「悄然连接」。首發將推出水波藍與宇宙黑兩款顏色，初期定價為25000[[日圓|日圓]]<ref name="WiiNintendo">{{cite web |date= 2010-09-29 |title= Nintendo Conference 2010 Converage: 3DS Launch Details Revealed |url= http://www.wiinintendo.net/2010/09/28/nintendo-conference-2010-coverage-3ds-japanese-launch-details-revealed-at-1-am-est-tonight/ |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20110107040747/http://www.wiinintendo.net/2010/09/28/nintendo-conference-2010-coverage-3ds-japanese-launch-details-revealed-at-1-am-est-tonight/ |archivedate= 2011-01-07 |publisher= WiiNintendo |accessdate= 2010-09-29 |deadurl= yes }}</ref>，而最終的主機設計也於此日確定。<ref>{{cite web |date=2010-09-29 |title=Nintendo 3DS Final Design |url=http://www.wiinintendo.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/09/3DS-final-design.png |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110724131108/http://www.wiinintendo.net/wp-content/uploads/2010/09/3DS-final-design.png |archivedate=2011-07-24 |publisher=WiiNintendo |accessdate=2010-09-29 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>

2011年1月19日，任天堂的北美分公司和歐洲分公司分别在[[美國|美國]][[紐約|紐約]]和[[荷蘭|荷蘭]][[阿姆斯特丹|阿姆斯特丹]]舉辦发布會 ，並在发布會中公布了許多与任天堂3DS有关的資訊。<ref>[http://live.nintendo3ds.nintendo-europe.com/index.html Nintendo 3DS Preview Event] {{Wayback|url=http://live.nintendo3ds.nintendo-europe.com/index.html |date=20110714184325 }} Nintendo of Europe</ref>发布会上公布了北美地區3DS的上市日期为2011年3月27日，定價為249.99[[美元|美元]]；歐洲地区的上市日期为2011年3月25日，定价则由當地零售商決定。但大多數零售商采用的售卖價格來自英國當地的初期售價：219.99[[英镑|英镑]]和229.99[[欧元|欧元]]。<ref>[http://www.gamesradar.com/nintendo-allowing-retailers-to-set-3ds-price-in-europe-good-luck-if-you-have-a-pre-order/ Nintendo allowing retailers to set 3DS price in Europe. Good luck if you have a pre-order] {{Wayback|url=http://www.gamesradar.com/nintendo-allowing-retailers-to-set-3ds-price-in-europe-good-luck-if-you-have-a-pre-order/ |date=20210205075548 }} Nintendo 3DS News at GamesRadar</ref>但某些零售商（例如[[亚马逊公司|亚马逊]]）已經把3DS的售价降得到比[[索尼电脑娱乐|索尼电脑娱乐]]（SCE）於2011年1月26日公布的PSP後續機[[PlayStation_Vita|PlayStation Vita]]還要低。<ref>{{cite web |last=Interactive |first=Disney |url=http://www.amazon.co.uk/dp/B004ISLDV0 |title=Nintendo 3DS at |publisher=Amazon.co.uk |date= |accessdate=2011-11-01 |archive-date=2020-06-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200628111614/https://www.amazon.co.uk/dp/B004ISLDV0 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

[[File:JR秋葉原駅_構内_Nintendo_3DS_体験コーナー.jpg|left]]
日本任天堂本部於2011年1月8日到10日，舉辦了3DS體驗會「Nintendo World 2011」並公布了首發陣容。而英國任天堂於2011年2月在英國舉辦了四場名為「眼见为实（Believe Your Eyes）」的體驗會，最开始只邀請任天堂俱樂部的會員參加，之後向一般民眾开放報名。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nintendo.co.uk/NOE/en_GB/events_31044.html#get-events/h/e |title=Find out where you can try Nintendo 3DS near you! |accessdate=2011-02-06 |publisher=Nintendo }}{{dead link|date=2017年11月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>澳洲任天堂則於同年3月，在[[西田集團|西田集團]]旗下的購物中心舉辦了一些小规模體驗會。

=== 發售後 ===

====2011年====
日本當地的零售商和商家指出首發將釋出40萬部的3DS<ref>{{cite web |author=Matt Peckham |url=http://www.pcworld.com/article/220875/nintendo_3ds_sells_400000_in_japan_already_r4_hacked.html |title=Nintendo 3DS Sells 400,000 in Japan, Already R4 Hacked |publisher=PC World |date=2011-02-28 |accessdate=2011-02-28 |archive-date=2012-05-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120508182301/http://www.pcworld.com/article/220875/nintendo_3ds_sells_400000_in_japan_already_r4_hacked.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。首发游戏包括《[[实况足球_3D足球|实况足球 3D足球]]》、《[[超级街头霸王IV_3D|超级街头霸王IV 3D]]》、《[[戰國無雙_編年史|戰國無雙 編年史]]》、《[[立體益智泡泡龍_3D|立體益智泡泡龍 3D]]》、《[[任天猫狗|任天猫狗]]》、《[[山脊赛车_3D|山脊赛车 3D]]》、《[[巨兽战争：恐龙_3D|巨兽战争：恐龙 3D]]》、《[[雷頓教授與奇蹟假面|雷頓教授與奇蹟假面]]》共8款<ref>{{cite news|title=任天堂新掌机3DS首发游戏阵容及价格公开|url=http://game.17173.com/content/2011-01-08/20110108130911535.shtml|accessdate=2013-09-03|newspaper=17173.com|date=2011-01-08|archive-date=2021-02-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210205075547/http://game.17173.com/content/2011-01-08/20110108130911535.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。而在2011年2月26日推出之後的當週週末，3DS總共賣出37.4萬-{zh-hans:台;zh-hk:部;zh-tw:台;}-主機。在這一週，首發陣容的《[[雷頓教授與奇蹟假面|雷頓教授與奇蹟假面]]》總共賣出11.9万套，使它成為首發陣容中最暢銷的遊戲。<ref name="top 20">{{cite web |url=http://www.4gamer.net/games/117/G011794/20110302065/ |title=Weekly consumer sales ranking |publisher=4Gamer.net |date=2011-02-27 |accessdate=2011-03-14 |archive-date=2015-05-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150513141138/http://www.4gamer.net/games/117/G011794/20110302065/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>同時它也是該週所有平台軟體銷量的第三名。

